overview: Here we hear the tale of a stepsister whose brother beats up a professor for her honor, a girl who catches her stepbrother reading her sex journal, a stepbrother whose volatile relationship with his sister turns into some heated sex, and an unpopular girl whose sexual attraction rises when the most popular guy in school becomes her stepbrother. It's jam-packed sibling action where resistance turns to lust in a matter of moments!
title: Sibling Seductions 3
